name: CatMouseWorld RICE
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
CatMouseWorld build on Arbitrum,Total supply of 50,000 NFTs. 10% cats and 90% mice in a completely randomised style. 100% Creative and completely on-chain game. 

What makes your project unique?
Interesting mint experience.

History of your project.
Started Apr-01-2023 10:01:22 AM +UTC

What’s next for your project?
Strengthen the community and make more interesting games.

What can your token be used for?
RICE is used for mint CatMouse NFT All consumption is fully burned.
